{"tid":1807250,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"點解到依刻工程界都唔肯罷工","createTime":"2020-01-01T17:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T06:48:58.000Z","uid":127511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"476e3c97f30de9aaa8be4a6473b7edd786c703b0","tid":1807250,"uid":127511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:08:28.000Z","msg":"身邊有唔少同事都黃，但就係冇人罷。<br />\n冇樓起攤唔攤換到個市"},{"pid":"7960c571c294f6298709bab876d0ec76302e4ee5","tid":1807250,"uid":201398,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:09:19.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"d8d6958cfc3e9f327cfd987bc8ef1432701baa31","tid":1807250,"uid":334861,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:09:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06fa2416ec3ec488616982c90c821462685f19f1","tid":1807250,"uid":34079,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:11:18.000Z","msg":"你係黃<br />\n但你有無諗過班師傅唔係<br />\n罷工唔係講出黎2隻字咁簡單<br />\n工會已經成立緊<br />\n叫埋啲人入"},{"pid":"eb7af716e4d11fdfeb21f48e05656ce79d0722c1","tid":1807250,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:12:27.000Z","msg":"工程同地產好密切<br />\n<br />\n有d直頭分部來"},{"pid":"327349d01fa2a16c859175fc615d9e6638d294ee","tid":1807250,"uid":224479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:17:59.000Z","msg":"工程界 明日大嶼 自己諗"},{"pid":"e3a70dd691c318d1f6f77229f8d14855c6b714dc","tid":1807250,"uid":182222,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"06fa2416ec3ec488616982c90c821462685f19f1","tid":1807250,"uid":34079,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:11:18.000Z","msg":"你係黃<br />\n但你有無諗過班師傅唔係<br />\n罷工唔係講出黎2隻字咁簡單<br />\n工會已經成立緊<br />\n叫埋啲人入"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:19:48.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n工會喺工程界尤其重要<br />\n班師傅手停口停<br />\n後生工程師驚俾大老世清算<br />\n一定要壯大工會既勢力先可以搞到罷工<br />\n工程界既工會喺最重要既工會之一，原因有兩個：<br />\n1. 工程界人數夠多，client+ consultant + contractor ,再加埋測量等界別係有機會做到人數最多既工會<br />\n2. 工程界項目資金夠多，其他行業有幾可一單proj值幾十億，工程界一唔夠人撈成本即刻貴幾倍，俾到壓力政府、發展商"},{"pid":"b123307bef0159dd698b618a72cd48d8c2acb700","tid":1807250,"uid":223525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:22:09.000Z","msg":"工程做得愈高層都偏藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4409772e6857b87d4a95bdefd1a43ff5adb12d6","tid":1807250,"uid":296203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:24:08.000Z","msg":"有冇邊個工程界工會值得入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c777780871bca9373e545b2315aa4092e2134d","tid":1807250,"uid":9942,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:29:36.000Z","msg":"遲一日起貨講緊罰幾十萬 唔係咁易架葉師傅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92c71c2bf064f135afb8c4f5333ab46315b96de","tid":1807250,"uid":1993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:32:20.000Z","msg":"工人8成藍<br />\n仲要手停口停<br />\n點會搞得成"},{"pid":"212f42c28291f35aa2de95d3a10a630d1b1bca7a","tid":1807250,"uid":180317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:38:33.000Z","msg":"後生工程師罷工有撚用咩<br />\n啲判頭同師傅好多藍到仆街<br />\n就算冇左工程師一頭半個月其實都冇好大影響"},{"pid":"f928355d78ea6aaae97894cb3fb32a3240af97bc","tid":1807250,"uid":105471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:40:24.000Z","msg":"想問普通做室內裝修既 計唔計係工程界工會 <br />\n識人做呢行 發現都唔少係深黃"},{"pid":"08c130fac8a6220f466e837658d918cfb34e0dce","tid":1807250,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:52:04.000Z","msg":"做工程 / 建築 呢行<br />\n本來對工人既就業保障就少, 隨時呢個項目完左就唔要你<br />\n而且做野要趕工期出貨<br />\n要搞罷工基本上係冇可能, 你罷完之後就到老板永久罷你工"},{"pid":"84a002ac7c6becaa46834f3629b4a9b551acba53","tid":1807250,"uid":7849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T20:07:50.000Z","msg":"好老實講，工程界罷工絕對唔會有好明顯同立即嘅影響力。<br />\n就算咩都停晒，最多咪個工期拖耐d，延期完工，個社會差你一棟樓/一條橋/etc 咩？<br />\n如果你講mains，咁個影響可能就會快d出現，但對比交通/醫療/金融果d嘅震撼性真係差得遠。<br />\n<br />\n不過我都希望各界無論影響有幾大，都要團結罷工，令政府冇得唔投降，團結先係最大力量"},{"pid":"80b5e4a89d0c00be93bf212968f4ccd646d50d48","tid":1807250,"uid":34079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4409772e6857b87d4a95bdefd1a43ff5adb12d6","tid":1807250,"uid":296203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:24:08.000Z","msg":"有冇邊個工程界工會值得入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T01:42:04.000Z","msg":"工會&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;五大訴求&gt;香港獨立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1806946\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1806946</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"623311d42d0e0cc00e0ed3f6f08022a33e232094","tid":1807250,"uid":38204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b123307bef0159dd698b618a72cd48d8c2acb700","tid":1807250,"uid":223525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:22:09.000Z","msg":"工程做得愈高層都偏藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:48:58.000Z","msg":"政府係最大客仔 邊到你唔藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}